#### --------------TASKS--------------
### getAllTasks
GET {{ endpoint }}/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### getAllTasksgetTasksWithFilters
GET {{ endpoint }}/api/tasks?status=IN_PROGRESS
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### getTaskById
GET {{ endpoint }}/api/tasks/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### createTask
# @name createTask
POST {{ endpoint }}/api/tasks
content-type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

title=Clean My Room&description=lots of stuff to do

### updateTask
PATCH {{ endpoint }}/api/tasks/{{{{id}}}}/status
content-type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

status=DONE


### deleteTask
DELETE  {{ endpoint }}/tasks/{{id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}